short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: View and filter CSV and Parquet files in your browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab Lab enables you to view, filter and analyze your CSV and Parquet data with AI.

The Tab Lab Chrome extension allows you to open CSV and Parquet files from a website straight into Tab Lab.
